Coordinator: Javier Mardonenes javiermardones@outlook.com

Forums: This working group will start with a channel on Zcash community and group in the Transifex platform to handle the translations

Statement of Purpose: The goal of this Working Group is to translate the Zcash Foundation for others languages than English.
We're going to start with the following languages:

- Portuguese
- Spanish
- Mandarim
- Russian

First steps:

- Open a public channel on the Chat to be called ZcashTranslation
- Open a channel in the Transifex platform called ZcashTranslation
- Recruit volunteers to make the translations
- Submit the translations to the http://z.cash.foundation

